00:49:13,800 --> 00:49:14,920
We're sorry to bother you.

569
00:49:15,040 --> 00:49:16,040
Please don't be. It's my pleasure.

570
00:49:17,200 --> 00:49:18,340
Please make yourselves at home.

571
00:49:18,380 --> 00:49:20,380
Let me know if you want anything.

572
00:49:21,480 --> 00:49:22,870
All the dishes look fantastic.

573
00:49:24,120 --> 00:49:27,000
Fah always says
this family cooks amazing food.

574
00:49:27,040 --> 00:49:29,320
I'll have to ask for your recipe one day.

575
00:49:29,360 --> 00:49:31,400
I'm willing to give it to you.

576
00:49:32,800 --> 00:49:34,440
Seeing the kids happy

577
00:49:34,480 --> 00:49:35,920
puts my mind at ease.

578
00:49:35,960 --> 00:49:38,600
That's all we want as a parent.

579
00:49:40,840 --> 00:49:43,560
Muenfah is lucky to have met Teerak.

580
00:49:44,040 --> 00:49:47,120
I was worried
that he wouldn't open up to anyone.

581
00:49:47,440 --> 00:49:48,850
Thought he would end up alone.

582
00:49:48,890 --> 00:49:51,120
Whoa.

583
00:49:51,160 --> 00:49:52,520
Let's not get ahead of ourselves.

584
00:49:52,560 --> 00:49:53,520
Let's say...

585
00:49:53,620 --> 00:49:56,910
they're both lucky to have found each other.

586
00:49:59,840 --> 00:50:01,880
Let's dig in, shall we?

587
00:50:01,920 --> 00:50:04,400
The kids will hang out later, too.

588
00:50:04,560 --> 00:50:06,040
- Oh, yeah?
- That's right.

589
00:50:06,240 --> 00:50:09,480
You guys can leave after this meal.

590
00:50:09,520 --> 00:50:11,720
Dad and I will stay here

591
00:50:11,760 --> 00:50:14,360
and talk to Teerak's family.

592
00:50:14,840 --> 00:50:15,720
Please.

593
00:50:15,760 --> 00:50:17,140
Sure. Don't worry.

594
00:50:17,180 --> 00:50:17,990
Let's eat.

595
00:50:18,030 --> 00:50:21,720
Alright, let's have our dinner now.

596
00:50:21,760 --> 00:50:23,080
- Please enjoy.
- Let's eat.

597
00:50:23,120 --> 00:50:24,480
What should we try first?

598
00:50:24,520 --> 00:50:25,100
This one.

599
00:50:25,140 --> 00:50:25,760
- What is it?
- Satay...

600
00:50:25,800 --> 00:50:26,640
- Here.
- What is it?

601
00:50:26,680 --> 00:50:28,040
- Wow!
- Okay.

602
00:50:28,080 --> 00:50:29,400
Okay, take some.

603
00:50:29,440 --> 00:50:30,280
- Should Grandpa take some first?
- Grandpa, grab some.

604
00:50:30,320 --> 00:50:31,080
- Sure.
- Here you go.

605
00:50:31,120 --> 00:50:32,200
Here you are.

606
00:50:32,240 --> 00:50:33,480
- Do you want some sauce, too?
- Thank you.

607
00:50:33,520 --> 00:50:34,310
Have some, Dad.

608
00:50:34,350 --> 00:50:36,290
- Thank you.
- Thank you.

609
00:50:36,330 --> 00:50:38,420
- Thank you.
- Thank you.

610
00:50:39,000 --> 00:50:40,080
Rak, here.

611
00:50:41,440 --> 00:50:42,640
Let's get changed,

612
00:50:42,680 --> 00:50:43,760
or we'll be late.

613
00:50:43,800 --> 00:50:45,840
No one takes longer than you.

614
00:50:45,880 --> 00:50:46,880
Hurry.

615
00:50:48,560 --> 00:50:50,160
Come on, I've already put on my makeup.

616
00:50:50,600 --> 00:50:51,820
- Fah.
- Yes?

617
00:50:52,400 --> 00:50:53,840
I have a surprise for you.

618
00:50:54,160 --> 00:50:55,080
What is it?

619
00:50:56,400 --> 00:50:57,400
Here!

620
00:51:02,000 --> 00:51:03,200
Do you like it?

621
00:51:04,160 --> 00:51:05,350
I love it.

622
00:51:06,000 --> 00:51:06,720
Right,

623
00:51:07,200 --> 00:51:08,680
I also have a surprise for you.

624
00:51:09,040 --> 00:51:10,040
Show me.

625
00:51:10,480 --> 00:51:11,280
Not yet.

626
00:51:11,320 --> 00:51:12,120
What?

627
00:51:13,680 --> 00:51:15,120
I'll show you when we're on the cruise.

628
00:51:16,040 --> 00:51:17,260
Okay.

629
00:51:17,300 --> 00:51:18,720
Let's go get changed, shall we?

630
00:51:19,840 --> 00:51:20,790
Let's go.

631
00:51:20,830 --> 00:51:23,030
Where are your clothes?

632
00:51:23,240 --> 00:51:24,240
In the car.

633
00:51:29,000 --> 00:51:31,590
Why is it taking so long? I'm starving.

634
00:51:31,800 --> 00:51:33,990
Jeez, why would you be upset?

635
00:51:34,960 --> 00:51:37,560
I told you to have some food before we came,
but you didn't listen.

636
00:51:39,360 --> 00:51:40,680
Can you stop being so fussy now?

637
00:51:41,120 --> 00:51:42,560
I've never been mean to you,

638
00:51:42,600 --> 00:51:43,800
but you're going too far.

639
00:51:45,080 --> 00:51:46,080
Fine,

640
00:51:46,960 --> 00:51:49,960
I'll let you have something tasty tonight.

641
00:51:54,560 --> 00:51:55,960
After the party, though.

642
00:51:56,880 --> 00:51:58,400
Tempting me and running away,

643
00:51:58,440 --> 00:51:59,320
lover boy?

644
00:51:59,760 --> 00:52:02,060
What's wrong with it?
I'm trying to be hard to get.

645
00:52:03,280 --> 00:52:04,440
What's really on your mind?

646
00:52:06,480 --> 00:52:07,760
"Calm down, Hia.

647
00:52:07,880 --> 00:52:09,400
You can't let him get you that easily."

648
00:52:09,440 --> 00:52:11,360
Wait, no.

649
00:52:12,120 --> 00:52:13,760
I heard all of that.

650
00:52:15,960 --> 00:52:17,480
It's surprising you're acting this way.

651
00:52:17,680 --> 00:52:18,680
Keep doing it, okay?

652
00:52:19,080 --> 00:52:20,080
It's adorable.

653
00:52:20,520 --> 00:52:21,680
Do you like it?

654
00:52:22,240 --> 00:52:23,640
It makes my heart skip a beat.

655
00:52:24,320 --> 00:52:25,320
What do you think?

656
00:52:26,880 --> 00:52:28,880
I'm the best.

657
00:52:31,000 --> 00:52:32,500
Give me a reward, big boy.

658
00:52:41,440 --> 00:52:44,040
When it comes to you,
I have no reason to say no.

659
00:52:44,440 --> 00:52:45,440
I'm willing to do anything,

660
00:52:46,200 --> 00:52:47,040
asshole.

661
00:52:48,600 --> 00:52:50,240
So you can speak your mind now?

662
00:52:50,640 --> 00:52:53,830
It should be me saying that to you.

663
00:52:54,480 --> 00:52:56,680
Our communication skills are improving,
and so are our kisses.

664
00:56:49,680 --> 00:56:51,260
When did you set all of this up?

665
00:56:52,320 --> 00:56:53,400
It's a secret.

666
00:56:53,600 --> 00:56:54,600
Do you like it?

667
00:56:58,120 --> 00:56:59,520
It's beautiful.

668
00:57:02,000 --> 00:57:03,400
I've got you a gift.

669
00:57:21,560 --> 00:57:24,760
[A gift for "Teerak"]

670
00:57:26,400 --> 00:57:32,000
♫It feels like the same old,
same old, familiar days♫

671
00:57:33,000 --> 00:57:39,320
♫There's something
that makes my heart drift away♫

672
00:57:39,600 --> 00:57:45,000
♫These familiar scenes
never fail to fascinate me, I dare say♫

673
00:57:46,070 --> 00:57:52,070
♫They always make my heart return to the first day♫

674
00:57:52,230 --> 00:57:55,550
♫Every time you smile, it always makes me shy♫

675
00:57:55,590 --> 00:57:58,870
♫Seeking for your sight, my thoughts fly♫

676
00:57:58,910 --> 00:58:02,150
♫I wish to stop the time, never saying goodbye♫

677
00:58:02,190 --> 00:58:04,590
♫Fall and fall in love♫

678
00:58:04,630 --> 00:58:09,830
♫How many more times will I fall for you?♫

679
00:58:09,870 --> 00:58:13,630
♫You always make my heart feel true♫

680
00:58:13,670 --> 00:58:17,680
♫You're the one, my love's always been for you♫

681
00:58:17,720 --> 00:58:23,080
♫For the rest of my life,
I'll spend each day loving you♫

682
00:58:23,120 --> 00:58:27,720
♫No matter how long or what we go through,♫

683
00:58:28,160 --> 00:58:33,560
♫I'll keep falling in love if it's with you♫

684
00:58:36,720 --> 00:58:43,520
♫Fall and fall in love, love, love, love♫

685
00:58:55,200 --> 00:58:57,240
Did you do all the editing?

686
00:58:57,420 --> 00:58:58,630
Yes, I did.

687
00:58:59,440 --> 00:59:01,160
I made this for you.

688
00:59:03,040 --> 00:59:04,040
Thank you so much.

689
00:59:04,960 --> 00:59:06,170
I really like it.

690
00:59:07,120 --> 00:59:08,930
There's one more thing I have for you.

691
00:59:21,200 --> 00:59:22,440
Is this for me?

692
00:59:22,760 --> 00:59:23,760
Yes.

693
00:59:24,360 --> 00:59:25,520
Try it on.

694
00:59:44,280 --> 00:59:45,560
Thank you so much.

695
00:59:46,500 --> 00:59:48,800
Thank you, too, for agreeing to be my boyfriend.

696
00:59:50,520 --> 00:59:51,640
Not just "agreeing."

697
00:59:52,120 --> 00:59:53,320
I love you.

698
00:59:55,000 --> 00:59:55,990
I'm into you.

699
00:59:56,030 --> 00:59:58,230
Whether it's a bright day or a stormy one,

700
00:59:58,720 --> 01:00:00,130
through every high and low,

701
01:00:00,720 --> 01:00:03,520
you'll always be my sky.

702
01:00:06,320 --> 01:00:08,320
From now on,

703
01:00:08,920 --> 01:00:11,320
I'll call you...

704
01:00:12,840 --> 01:00:14,000
my "Sky."

705
01:00:15,880 --> 01:00:17,060
So...

706
01:00:18,080 --> 01:00:20,120
I'll call you my "Sea."

707
01:00:38,520 --> 01:00:40,320
I never wished for anything on New Year's,

708
01:00:41,360 --> 01:00:42,860
but this year,

709
01:00:45,040 --> 01:00:48,640
I wish for us to wake up together
every morning,

710
01:00:52,360 --> 01:00:55,360
share smiles every day,

711
01:00:57,720 --> 01:00:59,320
and stay together

712
01:01:00,280 --> 01:01:02,840
through every moment, good or bad.

713
01:01:03,440 --> 01:01:05,440
I love you, my Sea.

714
01:01:06,120 --> 01:01:07,320
I really do.

715
01:01:07,800 --> 01:01:09,960
I love you so much, too, my Sky.

716
01:01:40,710 --> 01:01:42,400
What are you doing?

717
01:01:51,160 --> 01:01:52,760
Look at that, Fah.

718
01:01:54,240 --> 01:01:55,480
They're stunning.
